Understanding Microsoft Dynamics 365
Microsoft Dynamics 365 is an integrated suite of applications designed to manage core business functions such as sales, customer service, finance, operations, and human resources. It combines the power of customer relationship management (CRM) and enterprise resource planning (ERP) into a single, cloud-based platform, enabling businesses to streamline processes, improve efficiency, and enhance customer engagement.

